        Parameters:
        amp60 - The ampacity of this copper conductor with an insulation rated for 60°C
        amp75 - The ampacity of this copper conductor with an insulation rated for 75°C
        amp90 - The ampacity of this copper conductor with an insulation rated for 90°C
        resInPVCCond - The AC resistance of this copper conductor when used in a PVC conduit
        resInALCond - The AC resistance of this copper conductor when used in an aluminum conduit
        resInSteelCond - The AC resistance of this copper conductor when used in a steel conduit
        cuResDCUncoated - The DC resistance of this copper uncoated conductor
        cuResDCCoated - The DC resistance of this copper coated conductor
